Summary: I saw an huge ball of strobing light. It hovered then zipped away at very high speed.
divs: Sighting Details I was driving eastbound through Louisiana on Interstate 10. It was night time and I saw a huge ball of light hovering just over the trees. It was far away but very big, and it was strobing. It then then zipped away in a westward direction at very high speed.
